  "detailed_description": "<h1>DEVELOPER NOTES:</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a puzzle-heavy, slow-paced methodical game! If that's not something you think you'll like, the game might not be for you.</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Lies We Tell Ourselves</strong> is an <strong>episodic first person psychological action-adventure game</strong> with <strong>introspective/horror elements</strong> and a focus on <strong>subtle storytelling</strong> and <strong>atmosphere</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/67611bb130c941c2998fa718072288dc.poster.avif?t=1748781147\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/67611bb130c941c2998fa718072288dc.webm?t=1748781147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/67611bb130c941c2998fa718072288dc.mp4?t=1748781147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > An <strong>action-adventure experience</strong> that can be enjoyed by horror and non-horror fans. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Each episode is a carefully crafted blend of <strong>narrative</strong>, <strong>puzzles</strong>, <strong>exploration</strong> and even <strong>boss fights</strong>. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>A weird, rich story arc</strong>, with enough subtlety to let players build their own interpretation and meaning. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Challenging but fair puzzles</strong> that require observation, understanding and a bit of abstraction to be solved. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Mature and disturbing themes</strong>, but handled with respect and tact, rather than just for shock value.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each episode offers <strong>around 2 hours worth of gameplay</strong> which builds on the main story arc. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/dff59cc3a1792e6f08c4d1d8ca5bd10c.poster.avif?t=1748781147\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/dff59cc3a1792e6f08c4d1d8ca5bd10c.webm?t=1748781147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/dff59cc3a1792e6f08c4d1d8ca5bd10c.mp4?t=1748781147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A SUPERNATURAL STORY OF CHOICE AND CONSEQUENCE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the world of Vincent Arno, a man whose comfortable life is shattered on his 27th birthday, when a mysterious presence challenges his true nature. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/f82d2ade98dda62d165df3e8929b267b.poster.avif?t=1748781147\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/f82d2ade98dda62d165df3e8929b267b.webm?t=1748781147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/f82d2ade98dda62d165df3e8929b267b.mp4?t=1748781147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore Vincent's complex adult personality shaped by past choices, guiding him through a surreal introspective odyssey of self-discovery and moral ambiguity. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/b71a662986e0ab12c9c886032c7805a8.poster.avif?t=1748781147\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/b71a662986e0ab12c9c886032c7805a8.webm?t=1748781147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/b71a662986e0ab12c9c886032c7805a8.mp4?t=1748781147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover hidden truths in this thought-provoking adventure where the boundary between perception and reality is as fragile as the lies we tell ourselves. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/059dc036c0041bd6d322839f32b46546.poster.avif?t=1748781147\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/059dc036c0041bd6d322839f32b46546.webm?t=1748781147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176460/extras/059dc036c0041bd6d322839f32b46546.mp4?t=1748781147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
